KitKat::

She groaned as she started to come around. She opened her optics 
slightly and felt the machine repair her systems.  She glanced out 
the window and sighed.  She groaned in pain as the CR chamber started 
fixing her exterior body form.  She winced as the chamber started to 
make new skin and fur for her form. "ooohhhh" as a soft moan escaped 
from her mouth.
